    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has plenty of life left for its next owner! Whether you're commuting or hitting the road for a trip, this car is ready to go. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to a good home. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
