    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and variable double-VANOS for a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement to mitigate common fatigue, while the 6-speed manual transmission provides precise, tactile engagement. Power is managed via the factory variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension maintains its signature damping profile, offering the communicative feedback and neutral balance that defines this platform. A robust, performance-ready driver\u2019s car with all major mechanical vulnerabilities addressed.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 37
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
