    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel well\u2014typical for a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather upholstery is soft and free of tears, showing only slight softening of the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display functions perfectly, including the ice-cold dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, the car is in robust health; the engine idles quietly, shifts are crisp and seamless, and the suspension remains tight through the corners. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, and I have the service logs ready for your review. With deep tread remaining on all four tires and recent brake service, this car is ready for its next chapter without any immediate maintenance needs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
